          <div class="faq-answer">Plausible is a lightweight, privacy-first web analytics tool built as an open-source alternative to Google Analytics. Founded in 2019 in Estonia, it serves 15,000+ paying subscribers tracking 500,000+ sites. The script is under 1KB, sets no cookies, stores no personal data, and runs on EU servers.</div>
